SUMMARY:Steve Flemming's Love Songs that Stir the Soul (Friday March 6th) 
DESCRIPTION:Soul City Social Club (Toronto\, Canada)\nHello everyone\,\n\n
 Please join us **on zoom** for a fun\, relaxing and inspiring evening with
  **Love Songs that Stir the Soul.**\n\nSongs that I have written for well 
 over 35 years.\nYou will love what you hear! :)\nNew songs every week\, in
 cluding some of our favorites!\n\n\\*You are welcome to join us any time a
 fter 8:30 pm (Eastern Time)\n\\*You are also welcome to come on later in t
 he evening as well\n**\\*\\*Attend for free if you like - if it's your fir
 st time attending :)**\n\nEvent Details below:\n\nSincerely\,\n\nSteve Fle
 mming\n(Songwriter/Producer/Host)\n\nEvent Details:\n**Steve Flemming's Lo
 ve Songs that Stir the Soul (Friday\, March 6th)**\n**(on Zoom)**\n\n\\*Or
 iginal Lyrics and Songs by Songwriter and Producer Steve Flemming\n\n\\*St
 ory songs\, love songs\, spiritual songs\, songs about nature\, our cultur
 e\, our past\, our future\, relationships and our lives\n\nI'll be playing
  a mix of songs using a fusion of mixed genres like\, **Folk\, Traditional
  Folk\, Country\, Blue Grass\, Singer Song Writer\, Soft Rock\, Easy Liste
 ning\, Classic Rock\, R & B\, Gospel\, Pop\, Adult Contemporary\, Indie Ro
 ck/Po**p and many others genres too. So please sit back and get ready to h
 ave an amazing auditory experience in the comforts of your own home :)\n\n
 \\*You can come on and off at any time during the night- starting at 8:30 
 pm\n\n**About Steve Flemming:**\nHighly influenced by the great singer son
 gwriters of the 50s\, 60s\, 70s\, 80s and 90s. I have been writing my own 
 songs since 1990. Songs about life\, love\, loss\, hope\, faith\, joy\, ro
 mance\, memories\, spirituality and heartbreak. Songs that are universal\,
  heartfelt and often relevant to the lives of many others.\n\n\\-\\-\\-\\-
 \\-\\-\\-\\-\n**Event Fee:**\n\n**Pay What You Can: (P.W.Y.C)**\nYou can k
 indly send through e transfer or pay pal to:\n**steveflemming11@gmail.com*
 *\n\n-Anything you can contribute is greatly appreciated to help support t
 his meaningful musical endeavor and song loving community\n\n\\-\\-\\-\\-\
 \-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\n**Zoom lin
 k:**\n\nhttps://us04web.zoom.us/j/495043928\n\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\
 -\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\n\n**Testimonials from Past Events:*
 *\nYour songs are wonder-full\, speak to emotions\, experiences and moment
 s we've all felt and lived. S. B.\nSteve Flemming is an amazing songwriter
  whose lyrics stir the soul. He transforms everyday thoughts and life into
  beautiful poetry and magical tunes. Amazing stuff yet again Steve. - L.L.
 \nSteve\, thank you for a night of heartfelt\, exhilarating\, and inspirin
 g music.\nV.R.\nThanks for having me my friend. I love your words\, they c
 alm me and energize me at the same time I'll look forward to your next inv
 ite\nM.Z.\nThese great songs definitely helped me to decompress after a lo
 ng day. Keep up the song writing Steve\, these are great! - S.S.\nThank yo
 u so much for a relaxing evening and sharing your inspiring music Steve! I
  am excited to hear more and I hope you do this again!! - C.B\nLovely song
 s and a great vibe with wonderful people. I couldn’t have asked for a be
 tter way to close my day. Huge thanks Steve\, for inviting me! I truly enj
 oyed every moment! - N.A.\nThe lyrics are amazing. From the heart...\nThan
 ks Steve for the amazing tunes. I'm truly blown away. Very glad I joined.\
 n\\- E\\.E\\.\n\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-
