SUMMARY:The SATURDAY NIGHT ALL GREEN ST. PADDY'S BASH! (Pubs\, Band\, DJ &
  Dancing)
DESCRIPTION:Soul City Social Club (Toronto\, Canada)\nHello everyone\,\n\n
 **Kindly Read Carefully:**\n\nPlease join us for a unique **St. Paddy's** 
 experience as we hit\, not one but two great places to mix\, mingle and da
 nce the night away with Live Music\, Band\, DJ and awesome people!\n\nFirs
 t we will meet at ***Duke of Kent (2nd Floor) You can ask the hostess at t
 he front to direct you to Steve's group upstairs)*** (Conveniently located
  extremely close Yonge & Eglinton corner. (2 minute walk north from the su
 bway station)\n\nThe next venue is only minutes away from there (secret lo
 cation)\n\n**Where to Meet us?**\n**Duke of Kent:** You will be directed u
 pstairs to there cool party room area :)\n**Date:** Saturday March 14th\, 
 2026\n**Address:** 2315 Yonge Street Toronto\, ON M4P 2X9\n**Arrive betwee
 n:** 6:00 pm and 7:45 pm (if you can)\n(Encouraged earlier rather than lat
 er to have a chance to meet everyone and soak up a great Saturday night)\n
 \n**Highlights:**\n\\*Reserved tables and seating for dinner\, cocktails a
 nd mingling\n\\*Venue is very close to the Yonge and Eglinton subway stati
 on\n\\*Ice breaker game to make it easy to meet and connect with everyone 
 :)\n\\*A fun game to win complimentary beverages :)\n\\*Live Music (Band) 
 (DJ) and dancing at our second secret location\n\n\\*Dress casual or dress
  up if you like :)\n**DRESS IN Green and have a Chance to win Sweets and T
 reats :)**\n\n-Joined by my other social groups too\; so we can anticipate
  an awesome St. Paddy's Bash to remember!\n\n\\*One beverage or appetizer 
 minimum at the first and second location-(No loitering please)\nThank you 
 very much and remember to Tip your Servers :)\n\\*a 3rd venue may be an op
 tion too depending on how everyone is feeling :)\n\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\n\nEv
 ent Details below:\n\nSteve Flemming\n(Organizer/Host)\nhttps://www.meetup
 .com/soulcity/\n\n\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\nEvent Details:\n**
 The SATURDAY NIGHT ALL GREEN ST. PADDY'S BASH!**\n**(Pubs\, Band\, DJ & Da
 ncing)**\n\n-We will meet ***upstairs in their party bar room area\;*** co
 nnect with everyone\, ice breaker game\, socialize\, share some laughs\, t
 hen make our way new our surprise location with live music\, DJ\, super fu
 n atmosphere\, great people and dancing :)\n\\*Plan to come for dinner too
  if you like at the first venue\, as tables will be reserved for everyone\
 n\n(All Venues will be close walking distance for us)\n\n\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\
 -\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\n**
 EVENT FEE:**\n\n**Night of Event- Saturday March 14th (Arrival Times)**\n\
 n**\\*Ladies and Gents- Dress in Green if you can :)**\n-10 dollars if you
  arrive between (6:00 pm and 7:30 pm)\n-15 dollars if you arrive between (
 7:31 pm and 8:50 pm)\n\nIf you arrive after that you will simply miss the 
 event :)\n**(cash or by e transfer to steveflemming11@gmail.com)**\n\n**DR
 ESS IN GREEN and have a Chance to Win! :)**\n\n\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-
 \\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-\\-
